          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Results of 180Ta-m activation by 60Co and 137Cs gamma",
                " rays were obtained by studying its depopulation.",
                "The 180Ta-g  activity  (T1/2 = 8.1 hour) was detected",
                " via Hf Ka X-rays.",
                "From that effective and  integrated  cross  sections",
                " were inferred for the reaction 180Ta-m(g,g')180Ta.",
                "The former was defined as ratio of  the  activity  to",
                " the  primary flux,  whereas for obtaining the latter",
                " the activity was to be related to the  flux  density",
                " taken  at  resonance  energy,  i.e.  energy  of  the",
                " activation level."
              ]
            }
          ],
